Name: dev scripts
Installation: sudo apt install build-essential libssl-dev libyaml-dev libffi-dev libreadline-dev zlib1g-dev

Name: Nerd Font
Installation: mkdir -p ~/.local/share/fonts && cd ~/.local/share/fonts && curl -fLo "Fira Code Regular Nerd Font Complete.ttf" https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts/raw/master/patched-fonts/FiraCode/Regular/complete/Fira%20Code%20Regular%20Nerd%20Font%20Complete.ttf

Name: eza
Installation: sudo apt install -y gpg && sudo mkdir -p /etc/apt/keyrings && wget -qO- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/eza-community/eza/main/deb.asc | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /etc/apt/keyrings/gierens.gpg && echo "deb [signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/gierens.gpg] http://deb.gierens.de stable main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/gierens.list && sudo chmod 644 /etc/apt/keyrings/gierens.gpg /etc/apt/sources.list.d/gierens.list && sudo apt update && sudo apt install -y eza

Name: asdf
Installation: git clone https://github.com/asdf-vm/asdf.git ~/.asdf --branch v0.11.3 && echo '. "$HOME/.asdf/asdf.sh"' >> ~/.bashrc && echo '. "$HOME/.asdf/completions/asdf.bash"' >> ~/.bashrc

Name: node
Installation: asdf plugin add nodejs https://github.com/asdf-vm/asdf-nodejs.git && asdf install nodejs latest && asdf global nodejs latest

Name: python
Installation: asdf plugin-add python && asdf install python 3.13.3 && asdf global python latest

Name: ruby
Installation: asdf plugin add ruby https://github.com/asdf-vm/asdf-ruby.git && asdf install ruby 3.1.3 && asdf global ruby 3.1.3

Name: rust
Installation: asdf plugin add rust https://github.com/code-lever/asdf-rust.git && asdf install rust latest && asdf global rust latest

Name: go
Installation: asdf plugin add golang https://github.com/kennyp/asdf-golang.git && asdf install golang latest && asdf global golang latest

Name: AnyDesk
Installation: wget -qO - https://keys.anydesk.com/repos/DEB-GPG-KEY | sudo apt-key add - && echo "deb http://deb.anydesk.com/ all main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/anydesk-stable.list && sudo apt update && sudo apt install anydesk
